nodes.text: Tara Strong (born February 12, 1973) is a Canadian actress who voiced Risha Drayen, Holiday, and other additional voices, in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic. Strong also provided additional voices in the film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker.
